{"tid":1403143,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"今日旺角嘅檢討","createTime":"2019-08-03T17:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T01:50:35.000Z","uid":50467,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2341b3421a62aef05de7c1d4d53ce622f550b688","tid":1403143,"uid":50467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:52:58.000Z","msg":"我覺得今日彌敦道遊擊唔到嘅原因<br />\n唔係前線唔肯走<br />\n係人太多走都走唔到<br />\n想走亦走唔得快<br />\n今晚喺佐敦啲人少啲，但仲可以即興快閃埋紅隧<br />\n結論係我覺得多區一齊行動<br />\n雖然人數分散咗喺各區，但可以做到個流動性"},{"pid":"a57490cb4775f65e4c45d07bfec06665a0711991","tid":1403143,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:53:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f3b39139e41a34c8ff913cafdd945ae9578bb17a","tid":1403143,"uid":50467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:53:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d118e0d695605974478261a81b2508e76fb556b","tid":1403143,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:54:08.000Z","msg":"和理又唔做哨兵<br />\n又原地行街想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n撤退仲塞死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852df9ad155c6d70204b4026d93fe24b5f7be587","tid":1403143,"uid":50467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:10:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2baafb57b2c7371737cd431a0dc557965ba8058d","tid":1403143,"uid":50467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:41:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb75cce7e8cdd8b4064a69348f452199ce85352e","tid":1403143,"uid":50467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:41:45.000Z","msg":"遊擊呀"},{"pid":"0a8da752e53868b1f8eda7019a319518c07c42b8","tid"